headline: Payfare Reaffirms its Recommendation that Shareholders Vote "FOR" the Transaction with Fiserv
summary: Payfare Inc. ("Payfare" or the "Company") (TSX: PAY) (OTCQX: PYFRF) today reiterated the unanimous recommendation of its Board of Directors (the "Board") that shareholders vote "FOR" the proposed arrangement agreement (the "Arrangement") with Fiserv, Inc. ("Fiserv") (NYSE: FI) and 1517452 B.C. Ltd. (the "Purchaser"), an affiliate of Fiserv.
